le</strong><span>. Which, in my opinion, is a feature.&#160;</span></p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20p=
x 0;"><span>Startup Prophecy NFTs are not shares in the company. They&#8217=
