I can&#8217;t know all of the different ways that people might run with the=
 idea, but there are a few categories of things I can see happening that ha=
ve little to do with the price of the NFTs themselves. Here are a few.&#160=
;</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin=
: 0 0 20px 0;"><strong>Broaden the Community of Supporters</strong></p><p s=
tyle=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20p=
x 0;"><span>Would Startup Prophecies broaden the community of supporters ar=
ound the most ambitious companies? Would artists and videographers and writ=
ers find rich new source material in companies aligned with their beliefs? =
Would companies themselves create </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/re=
